      <title>元宵赏烟花</title>
      <link>https://ioerr.github.io/posts/yuanxiao-shang-yanhua/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Feb 2009 18:39:40 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ioerr.github.io/posts/yuanxiao-shang-yanhua/</guid>
      <description>在元宵节央视大裤衩配楼着火的时候，我正在湘江边上欣赏另一出烟花表演。 州官放火，百姓点灯，真是其乐融融一派和谐啊。 江边的人群实在拥挤，沿江风光</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>在元宵节央视大裤衩配楼着火的时候，我正在湘江边上欣赏另一出烟花表演。<br>
州官放火，百姓点灯，真是其乐融融一派和谐啊。</p>
<p>江边的人群实在拥挤，沿江风光带的栏杆边上围了至少三层人，还不断有人下到江岸抢占有利位置。<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278581568/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3412/3278581568_e10ec5db7e.jpg" alt="看烟花的人群 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a><br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278577102/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3521/3278577102_a2170a927c.jpg" alt="看烟花的人群 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a></p>
<p>于是烟花燃放完毕后，场面就变得恐怖了，还好没有出现踩踏的事故。<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278649118/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3533/3278649118_64ef0bffaf.jpg" alt="看烟花的人群 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a></p>
<p>虽然到达的时间比较晚，却抢占了有利的地形拍照，只可惜满意的照片不多：<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278532884/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3470/3278532884_374052f4d5.jpg" alt="湘江上的元宵烟花 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a><br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278597018/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3387/3278597018_8bddd0d312.jpg" alt="湘江上的元宵烟花 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a></p>
<p>人群散去之后，就只有激光射灯在孤独的摇摆：<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278669478/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3313/3278669478_bd03a0570f.jpg" alt="IMG_6440 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a><br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278684378/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3472/3278684378_c6a0acccd2.jpg" alt="IMG_6445 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a></p>
<p>太平街的戏台非常难得的有表演，应该是《白蛇传》吧：<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3277911051/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3527/3277911051_dc536b4251.jpg" alt="白蛇传 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a></p>
<p>元宵节前一天在太平街口看到的正准备挂起来的灯笼：<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3277653611/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3453/3277653611_70d0321408.jpg" alt="灯笼 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/sets/72157613783847173">更多照片</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>除夕焰火</title>
      <link>https://ioerr.github.io/posts/chuxi-yanhuo/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Feb 2008 16:10:36 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ioerr.github.io/posts/chuxi-yanhuo/</guid>
      <description>除夕晚上跑出去练习拍摄焰火。周围的大型焰火不多，我又没有三角架，所以像打游击一般在小区走来走去，用2秒的曝光手持拍摄… 最开始是跑到天台上拍摄</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>除夕晚上跑出去练习拍摄焰火。周围的大型焰火不多，我又没有三角架，所以像打游击一般在小区走来走去，用2秒的曝光手持拍摄…</p>
<p>最开始是跑到天台上拍摄，结果发现爆炸点就在很近的同水平位置，还是前后夹击，加上无法拍摄到完整的焰火，为安全着想，没有呆多久就下来了。<br>
留下两张下半层后在窗户拍到的近距离焰火说明情况。<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/2248275007/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2322/2248275007_e328efbc09.jpg" alt="近距离爆开的烟花"  />
</a><br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/2248271057/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2394/2248271057_2e0611bb04.jpg" alt="近距离爆开的烟花"  />
</a></p>
<p>距离稍远一点但是被挡住的焰火。<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/2248266635/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2318/2248266635_351de4b500.jpg" alt="烟花"  />
</a></p>
<p>还是在楼下打游击容易抓到。<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/2249075642/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2022/2249075642_47234af34b.jpg" alt="烟花"  />
</a><br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/2248288591/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2010/2248288591_0e5c79cace.jpg" alt="烟花"  />
</a></p>
<p>可惜放烟花的人很少，不然多练练可以拍好一点。<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/2249089612/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2129/2249089612_e107becda8.jpg" alt="烟花"  />
</a><br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/2249105844/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2355/2249105844_ece306cc3d.jpg" alt="烟花"  />
</a><br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/2248304167/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2096/2248304167_186623ffb2.jpg" alt="烟花"  />
</a><br>
而且2秒的手持，不手抖才怪，天气又那么冷…</p>
<p>最后是黑暗中写字的游戏，但是人家只知道在空中乱舞，作为偷窥者我又不能指挥他们…<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/2249107480/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2389/2249107480_4b0daf6714.jpg" alt="烟花"  />
</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
